Issue ID: 114371
Issue Type: crash
Issue Commit: 71cfa381ef8c4fe659c67e8b2901d767e10f2aff
Issue Title: clang crashes on valid code at -O{2,3} on x86_64-linux-gnu:
Assertion `(I->use_empty() || all_of(I->uses(), [&](Use &U) { return isDeleted(
cast<Instruction>(U.getUser())); })) && "trying to erase instruction with
users."' failed
