│ containing reduction operations that should be ignored during scalar        │
│ cleanup. However, in the `vectorizeTree` function, when `UserIgnoreList` is │
│ provided, the code attempts to replace uses of to-be-deleted instructions   │
│ with poison values, but only for users in the `UserIgnoreList`. The problem │
│ is that the horizontal reduction logic doesn't properly account for all     │
