│ on `%tobool` through the chain.\n\nThe core issue is in the                 │
│ `removeInstructionsAndOperands` function's handling of the                  │
│ `UserIgnoreList`. The current logic assumes that all users of to-be-deleted │
│ instructions are either in the vectorization tree or in the ignore list,    │
